{"tid":2495218,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聶德權：有未簽聲明公務員稱聲明內容損言論自由　大部分已被停職","createTime":"2021-04-19T05:10:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T05:45:59.000Z","uid":20933,"like":8,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"bd8723ca33d04ac7bc79440751c009e05b79ee8b","tid":2495218,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:10:38.000Z","msg":"公務員事務局長聶德權表示，相關部門已去信要求未簽署擁護《基本法》聲明的129名公務員解釋原因，部分人在回覆中提到，認為聲明內容損害言論自由，亦有人指不同意聲明內容，或內容與持有外國護照有衝突。公務員事務局常任秘書長楊何蓓茵表示，大部分涉事的公務員因為解釋不被接納，已被停職。 <br />\n<br />\n聶德權又指，計劃下月落實並公布按非公務員條款聘用的政府僱員，都要簽署聲明，包括合約員工及退休後再獲聘人員，目前不會要求資助機構員工宣誓或簽署聲明。 <br />\n<br />\n民建聯何俊彥指，對不簽署聲名的公務員感到「火滾」，認為代表入職多年以來一直無盡忠職守，要求當局交代有無拒絕簽署而離職的公務員，日後仍能領取長俸。<br />\n<br />\n工聯會陸頌雄指，拒絕簽署的公務員起碼是「擺明車馬」坦白，反而擔心簽署的人陽奉陰違，「發誓當食生菜」，日後繼續拉政府後腿。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2387836\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2387836&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx6HDOfwBZUVptSzBKRgi4hA%3D&h=d41053b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2387836</a>"},{"pid":"3f532c802a2a3aedc75ba33e0be4c35ba52557db","tid":2495218,"uid":383914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:14:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/short.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efcfc5d95f70b9270f69978f7438e0229fc5e480","tid":2495218,"uid":220252,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:16:33.000Z","msg":"少部份係咪佢自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2732559